<h2>Pay Over Time with Affirm</h2>
<div class="field field--name-field-description field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden field--item"><p>Envoyage has partnered with Affirm to offer flexible payment options, allowing you to book now and pay over time with no late or hidden fees. When you're ready to book, connect with an advisor and request Affirm as your payment method. Pick the payment plan that works best for you with fixed monthly installments from three, six, 12 or 18 months*. Subject to eligibility.</p>
</div>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><a class="btn btn-primary affirm-site-modal" href="" aria-label="SEE IF YOU PREQUALIFY - Affirm Financing (opens in modal)" style="cursor: pointer; margin-bottom: 10px;">See If You Prequalify</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/affirm" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-bottom: 10px;">Learn about Affirm</a></p>

<p><a href="/affirm-disclosure">Terms and conditions apply.</a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
